{"tid":1952017,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"科大校長論壇與支那人發生碰撞既手足被控傷人17","createTime":"2020-03-31T10:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T11:42:32.000Z","uid":72511,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8376e41215b788dda697e9d292f3dd8958d5c0","tid":1952017,"uid":72511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:41:27.000Z","msg":"《昨被登門拘捕科大同學今午提堂》<br />\n<br />\n一名科大同學涉嫌於十一月六日之校長論壇與他人發生碰撞，昨日被登門拘捕，今午提堂。本會代表到場旁聽，同學被控「傷人或對他人身體加以嚴重傷害」，該指控屬侵害人身罪中最嚴重之一。同學獲准以五千港元保釋，期間不准離港，每逢星期三六需到警處報到。本會已代為繳付保釋金，亦將繼續提供所需援助。<br />\n<br />\n同學將在五月二十六日再次提堂，本會呼籲科大人到場旁聽支持。<br />\n<br />\n科大學生會<br />\n二零二零年三月三十一日"},{"pid":"4999aaa45e565827539b07d4cbd2d9027f3991e1","tid":1952017,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"好似19嚟"},{"pid":"9a11831a2cd272a99ccf41d2eb3f960b791208ad","tid":1952017,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:46:37.000Z","msg":"狗撞人就冇罪？亂告"},{"pid":"46e8fef8b26844ad78760b52e97aa605000ae5a6","tid":1952017,"uid":72511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4999aaa45e565827539b07d4cbd2d9027f3991e1","tid":1952017,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"好似19嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:51:37.000Z","msg":"應該係19 頭先睇錯左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8fbf4176529b313dab36971e9631b399cb5241","tid":1952017,"uid":128514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"案發現場有冇CCTV?"},{"pid":"45213383a9f3e2f140e59d2c2d8fd05ff988a6c5","tid":1952017,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c8fbf4176529b313dab36971e9631b399cb5241","tid":1952017,"uid":128514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"案發現場有冇CCTV?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:59:19.000Z","msg":"【告急】呢一刻最逼切亦最有用嘅聯署<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<